    subtitle: '',
    content: '<div style="max-width:48rem;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ts-navy),var(--ts-blue));color:white;border-radius:1rem;padding:2rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"><p style="font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.7;">At T&S Traffic Control, we expect our traffic controllers to deal with all road users, pedestrians and clients with <strong>utmost respect and manners.</strong></p></div><div style="display:grid;gap:0.75rem;text-align:left;"><div style="background:var(--glass);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1rem 1.5rem;border-left:3px solid var(--ts-green);"><p style="font-style:italic;color:var(--text-secondary);">"Good morning/afternoon! Please wait here for a moment; I\'ll let you know when it\'s safe to go."</p></div><div style="background:var(--glass);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1rem 1.5rem;border-left:3px solid var(--ts-green);"><p style="font-style:italic;color:var(--text-secondary);">"Alright, you\'re good to go! Watch your step and have a great day!"</p></div><div style="background:var(--glass);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1rem 1.5rem;border-left:3px solid var(--ts-green);"><p style="font-style:italic;color:var(--text-secondary);">"Thanks for your patience! You can cross now — stay safe!"</p></div></div><p style="color:var(--text-secondary);margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.05rem;">Being polite and using a friendly tone creates an <strong>impactful difference.</strong></p></div>',
