    content: '<div style="max-width:48rem;margin:0 auto;"><div style="background:var(--ts-red);color:white;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;"><p style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Sexual Harassment Policy</p><div style="display:grid;gap:0.5rem;font-size:1rem;opacity:0.9;"><p>• Zero tolerance for inappropriate jokes, comments, touching, or advances</p><p>• Any report is taken seriously and investigated confidentially</p><p>• Offenders may be removed from site or face termination</p></div></div><div style="background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;"><p style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Relationships on Site</p><div style="display:grid;gap:0.5rem;color:var(--text-secondary);"><p>• Any romantic relationships between team members must be declared to management</p><p>• No displays of affection on site — keep it professional</p><p>• Managers/supervisors cannot be in relationships with direct subordinates</p></div></div><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ts-navy),var(--ts-blue));color:white;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.25rem;text-align:center;"><p style="font-weight:600;">Speak to the HR manager or designated contact officer. Anonymous reports can also be made.</p></div></div>',
