    content: '<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;max-width:52rem;margin:0 auto;"><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b91c1c,#dc2626);color:white;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">P</p><p style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">PULL</p><p style="font-size:0.9rem;opacity:0.9;">Pull pin at the top, breaking the seal. Test the extinguisher aiming away from you.</p></div><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c2410c,#ea580c);color:white;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">A</p><p style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">AIM</p><p style="font-size:0.9rem;opacity:0.9;">Approach from a safe distance. Aim the nozzle at the base of the fire.</p></div><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#15803d,#16a34a);color:white;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">S</p><p style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">SQUEEZE</p><p style="font-size:0.9rem;opacity:0.9;">Squeeze the handles together to discharge. Release to stop.</p></div><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#2563eb);color:white;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">S</p><p style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">SWEEP</p><p style="font-size:0.9rem;opacity:0.9;">Sweep the nozzle side to side at the base of the flames.</p></div></div>',
